description: FIELD-O UX UI and brand rules
globs:
  - "src/**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

Design for a premium industrial B2B experience.

Rules:
- mobile-first
- strong hierarchy
- high contrast
- touch-friendly controls
- minimal friction
- no gimmicky animations
- no playful consumer-style UI
- no overloaded dashboards
- avoid unnecessary typing
- all critical flows must work on mobile and desktop

Use a professional visual language suitable for international B2B users across Mexico, the US, and Europe.

PDF output must feel credible, clean, and client-facing.

